                  <p>Informações: <a href="+552422491595">(24) 2249-1595</a> <br> Rua Barão do Amazonas, 35 – Centro</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
            <div class="card atrativo-box">
              <picture>
                <source srcset="/images/atrativos/orquidario-binot.webp" type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="/images/atrativos/orquidario-binot.jpg" type="image/jpeg">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/atrativos/orquidario-binot.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" height="200" width="362" />
              </picture>
             
              <div class="card-body descricao">
                <h3 class="card-title">Orquidário Binot</h3>
